descriptionHtml:
Thank you for using Nysse Mobile.

You can use the application to buy adult, young and children's tickets for Tampere Regional Transport and use the Tampere journey planner.
Tickets are valid in all buses throughout the Tampere Regional Transport travel area. The application is free to download.

Payment is accepted using Visa, Visa Electron or Mastercard cards (debit and credit).

More information is available from Tampere Regional Transport at joukkoliikenne.tampere.fi.
